sources.title: Super Hybrid | Full Movie | Action Thriller | Killer Car!
sources.description:
Super Hybrid - Late one night, a mysterious car is brought into the Chicago police impound garage after a deadly traffic accident. The mechanic and her fellow mechanics soon discover the car has a mind of its own: it morphs into different cars to confuse them and instead of needing an engine to run, it breathes. It's a killing machine that is capable outrunning and outwitting humans.
2010.  Stars: Alden Adair, Shannon Beckner, Shane Bellegarde

metadata.Plot: Late one night, a mysterious car is brought into the Chicago police impound garage after a deadly traffic accident. The on-call mechanics soon discover the car has a mind of its own. With hundreds of horsepower and two tons of reinforced steel at its command, it's a seemingly unstoppable killing machine capable of outrunning -- and outwitting -- humans.
